data.description: Nestled in the tranquil 55+ community of Sierra Dawn North step into your dream home with this inviting 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured gem. Unlike many other manufactured homes on the market, the selling price includes home and land. There are no park space rental fees, and an HOA of only $40 yearly. As you enter, you'll be greeted with living and dining areas that are seamlessly connected and feature custom-built ins that add both character and functionality to the space. With a separate private entrance, you find a stunning sunroom that floods the space with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere perfect for morning coffee or afternoon relaxation. For those moments when you desire a more private relaxation space, there's a second living room that offers tranquility and seclusion. Cooking enthusiasts will adore the accessible kitchen, complete with a walk-in pantry and ample storage space for all your culinary needs. The master bedroom is a true retreat, boasting an attached bathroom designed for luxury living. Enjoy a sunken tub for long, luxurious soaks, a separate stand-up shower for a quick refresh. The second bedroom offers the utmost convenience with its own attached bathroom featuring a shower-tub combination. Whether it's a guest or family member, they'll feel right at home. Step outside to your fenced-in yard, where privacy and security meet the great outdoors. Whether you have pets, love gardening, or simply enjoy the fresh air, this space is perfect for your needs. And, with two sheds, you'll have ample storage space for all your tools, equipment, and seasonal items. This property combines comfort, convenience, and style, creating a welcoming haven you'll love coming home to every day. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to make it your own.
